trans-unit.source: Specifies a rotation transformation.
trans-unit.target: Angir en rotasjon transformering.

trans-unit.source: Rotations in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_2d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-2d-md.md)] usually consist of two arguments: a point around which to rotate an object or set of objects, and a value in degrees or radians that determines the amount of rotation.
trans-unit.target: Rotasjoner i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_2d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-2d-md.md)] vanligvis bestå av to argumenter: et punkt som skal rotere et objekt eller settet med objekter, og en verdi i grader eller radianer som bestemmer hvor mye.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)], it is necessary to specify a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Vector3D> rather than a point around which to rotate.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)], må du angi en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Vector3D>i stedet for et punkt som skal roteres.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Vector3D>

trans-unit.source: Rotations in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] become more complicated when they are animated.
trans-unit.target: Rotasjoner i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] blir mer kompliserte når de er animerte.

trans-unit.source: To animate a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] rotation using RotateTransform3D, you can animate the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D.Angle%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D.Axis%2A> properties of an <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D>, or specify a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.QuaternionRotation3D> for the transform..
trans-unit.target: Å animere en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] rotasjon ved hjelp av RotateTransform3D, kan du animere den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D.Angle%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D.Axis%2A>Egenskaper for en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D>, eller angi en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.QuaternionRotation3D>for transformering..</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.QuaternionRotation3D> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D.Axis%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.AxisAngleRotation3D.Angle%2A>

trans-unit.source: Axis/angle rotations in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] are specified in degrees, not radians.
trans-unit.target: Akse/vinkel rotasjoner i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_3d](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] er angitt i grader ikke radianer.
